---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | WorkMultiple"
  description="WorkMultiple's terms of service. The terms that govern use of our website and products."
>
  <Header />

  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container content-inner">
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="page-meta">Effective March 4, 2026</p>

      <p>These terms govern your use of the WorkMultiple website and the products we offer. By using our website or purchasing our products, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use our website or purchase our products.</p>

      <h2>What We Offer</h2>
      <p>WorkMultiple publishes digital products (such as premium playbooks and guides) and free content (such as blog articles, tool comparisons, and tutorials) about using AI tools to automate business workflows. Our products are delivered digitally.</p>

      <h2>Digital Products</h2>
      <p>When you purchase a digital product (such as a playbook), you receive a personal, non-transferable license to use that product for your own business purposes. You may not redistribute, resell, or share the product with others. The content of our playbooks is copyrighted.</p>

      <h2>Refund Policy</h2>
      <p>Because our products are digital and delivered instantly, all sales are final. If you experience a technical issue with a product (such as a corrupted download), contact us and we will resolve it promptly.</p>

      <h2>Newsletter</h2>
      <p>By subscribing to our newsletter, you agree to receive periodic emails from us. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in any email we send. We will never sell or share your email address with third parties.</p>

      <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>Some of our content includes affiliate links to tools and services we recommend. If you purchase through these links, we may receive a commission at no additional cost to you. We only recommend tools we have personally tested. Affiliate relationships never influence our recommendations.</p>

      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>We stand behind the quality of our content and products, but we cannot guarantee specific business outcomes (such as revenue increases or time savings) resulting from following our guides. Our liability for any claim related to a product is limited to the amount you paid for that product.</p>

      <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All content on this website and in our products (including text, graphics, and design) is the property of WorkMultiple and is protected by copyright. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from our content without written permission.</p>

      <h2>Use of the Website</h2>
      <p>This website is provided for informational purposes and to allow you to learn about and purchase WorkMultiple products. You agree not to misuse the website, including by attempting to access it through automated means or interfering with its operation.</p>

      <h2>Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p>We may update these terms from time to time. If we make meaningful changes, we will update the effective date at the top of the page. Continued use of our website or products after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>

      <h2>Governing Law</h2>
      <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the United States. Any disputes will be resolved in accordance with those laws.</p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>Questions about these terms? Email us at <a href="mailto:emilio@workmultiple.com">emilio@workmultiple.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding: 4rem 0 6rem;
  }

  .content-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .page-meta {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #888888;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.7em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-border);
  }

  a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: rgba(233, 89, 74, 0.3);
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
